I

IMasteringService - Interface in com.kuka.med.mastering
Capability interface for mastering a robot from a robotics application in all operation modes.
invalidateMastering(int) - Method in interface com.kuka.med.mastering.IMasteringService
Invalidates the mastering of the specified joint.
isJointMastered(int) - Method in interface com.kuka.med.mastering.IMasteringService
Returns the mastering state of the specified joint, which must be 0 <= joint < number of robot joints.

M

MedApplicationCategory - Annotation Type in com.kuka.med.mastering
Task category that describes a robotic application that can be started even if a robot axis is unmastered.
